[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "くたくたぁ……宿への道のりが遠い～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01242",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "今日は色々あったもんね。\n武道会に賞金首の大捕物……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01243",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "イザナちゃんはそのどっちも参加したんだもん、\nたくさんお疲れさまだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01244",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "えへへ。まあ武道会で全部出し切っちゃって\n賞金首を追いかける時はバテバテだったけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01245",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "町娘Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あ、あの！　もしかして武道会に出てた\nイザナ選手ですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_711_036_01246",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "え？　あ、うん、そうですけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01247",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "町娘Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "きゃ～！　やっぱりイザナ様だ～！\nハンマーを振るう姿、素敵でした！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_712_036_01248",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "町娘Ｃ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "握手してください！　してくれたら\n手、一生洗いません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_713_036_01249",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "握手くらい、いいけど……手は洗ってね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01250",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "町娘Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あの、あの！　これにサインください！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_711_036_01251",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "サイン？　サインなんて……実は考えてあるんだよね。\n騎士団員になった時に練習しといてよかった～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01252",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うわあ、イザナちゃん大人気だなあ……\n武道会で大活躍だったもんねぇ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01253",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "嬢ちゃん、ちょっといい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01254",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あっ、あなたは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01255",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、別に襲ったりしない。逆に謝りにきたんだ。\nあの時は急だったんで、我ながら冷静じゃなかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01256",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "は、はぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01257",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "とはいえ、ここじゃ人目につくな……秘密の話だから、\n悪いけど場所を変えさせてくれないか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01258",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "分かりました。そんなに離れることはできませんが……\nあの、イザナちゃん、私ちょっとジョゼさんと話が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01259",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "うん、すぐ駆けつけられる位置にいてね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01260",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "はい、列になって並んで！\n最後尾の人は手を挙げて～！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さて……改めてになるが。本当にごめんね。\n強い言葉で脅迫して、君を不安にさせちゃった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01261",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "どうしても正体がバレたら困る相手がいて、\n慌ててあんな心にもないことを口走ってしまったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01262",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そう、だったんですか。\n何か事情があるんだなとは、思っていました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01263",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "この仮面をつけたジョゼの姿は、偽りでね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01264",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "本名は……ギヨームですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01265",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだ。俺の本当の名はギヨーム・カスターニュ。\nヌルスラの生まれでね、あの鷹とも顔見知りだったのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01266",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "けど、タイニーが来る時に俺の名を呼ばれちゃ\nたまらない。それでつい口を封じちゃったんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01267",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でもタイニーさん、\nあなたを探しているって話でしたよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01268",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "彼女には正体をバラせないんだ。黙っていてくれないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01269",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "頼む。レスナ・シュテルネンリヒト",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01270",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "何か事情があるなら、ぜひお力になりたく思います",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01271",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ありがと。でも、過去の話なんだ。\n時間を巻き戻せるなら、ぜひお願いしたいけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01272",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "すみません、それは……無理です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01273",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だよね。まぁ、詳しい事情については長くなるから、\nどこかで話すよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01274",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "彼女が真実を知ってもただ悲しくなるだけなんだ。\nだから、黙っていたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01275",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……分かりました。\nタイニーさんにはジョゼさんのこと、黙っておきます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01276",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ありがとう、感謝する。\n初めからこう頼めばよかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01277",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でも……そんな仮面だけでよくタイニーさんに\n正体がバレませんでしたね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01278",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "いや、この姿で再会した時に０．１秒で聞かれたよ。\nもしかしてギヨームお兄ちゃんかって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01279",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それで違うと否定したら信じてしまった。\nあの子は……純粋だから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01280",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、あはは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01281",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "なんだ、珍しい組み合わせだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01282",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……って、レスナさんと変てこ仮面さん？\nもしかして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01283",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ち、ちちち、違いますよ！\n決して秘密の相談ではなくて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01284",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "もしかして、二人は恋仲……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01285",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "烏白馬角です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01286",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "意味は分からないけど否定されたことは分かる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01287",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "まったく、他の誘拐犯がいないか見回っているのに\n紛らわしいことをするな。ほら、さっさと宿に帰れ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01288",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はいはい。それじゃ……レスナ、ありがとね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01289",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……変てこ仮面さん、私の行く先々で\nちょこちょこ見かけるんですよねえ……変な人です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01290",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
